short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Reverse image search to find cheaper prices! Right-click on an image and select 'Find Cheaper Price' to start the search.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Have you ever bought an item and later realized it was being sold for a fifth of the price on another website? Well, this extension helps you find that cheaper site by adding tools to Google Lens. Simply right click an image and click 'Find Cheaper Price'!
